SIMPLE: troth
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Troth
<hw>Troth</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[A variant of
<ets>truth</ets>. See <er>Truth</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Belief;
faith; fidelity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Bid her alight⟦br⟧
And her<qex>troth</qex> plight.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Truth; verity; veracity; <as>as, by my
<ex>troth</ex></as>.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In <qex>troth</qex>, thou art able to instruct gray hairs.</q>
<rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Betrothal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trothless</ent>⟦br⟧
